@{b}@{fg shine}AGA-Morph V2.1@{ub}@{fg text}                                                @{b}@{fg shine}AGA-Morph V2.1@{ub}@{fg text}

  In the edit window the points that are selected to be changed are shown.
  The seletected  points will  be marked  with a  cross, the  others with a
  small rectangle.  The position  of a point will  be changed  by just
  clicking on its new position.

